body:
Comment 6 by **tarmigan**: 
Oops, I think this may be either a goinstall issue or a me being stupid.

If I clean out the src/pkg/github.com/ajstarks/svgo directory before doing a goinstall
-a then svgo makes OK from the latest tip.  For some reason goinstall -a was not
updating or the old pkgs were not getting deleted.

I'll dig around some more and report back.
